short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays all the available ID Codes for the song Trust Fund.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
In Roblox, every audio item is attached to a unique ID code to identify it. As a result of this, every song has a unique ID code.

As a solution to this, Trust Fund Roblox ID extension will help you to find the ID Code of the song.

Before installing, you should understand why the collection of ID Codes is essential -
1. Roblox ID Codes can be removed due to copyright violation.
2. Multiple versions of the same song over Roblox Library.

All these reasons create a massive mess in collecting and saving the ID Codes of any song. This extension will provide you with all updated IDs for the song Trust Fund.

Install now and get all the ID Codes now!

✔️Updated IDs.
✔️IDs for every different versions of the song.
